{"tid":1596303,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"古天奴啤酒節舉杯：家的感覺","createTime":"2019-09-26T12:49:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T14:11:25.000Z","uid":322766,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0b68ffeb08bfe9d15c97936a3c3e4d9bfc7b0f09","tid":1596303,"uid":322766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:49:01.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】拜仁慕尼黑球員出席一年一度的啤酒節，巴西球星古天奴頻頻與隊友碰杯慶祝。<br />\n<br />\n一年一度的慕尼黑啤酒節又再舉行，今夏加盟拜仁慕尼黑的古天奴（Philippe Coutinho）首度參與該傳統大節日。古天奴和隊友們穿上傳統的巴伐利亞服裝出席啤酒節，同枱的還有盧卡靴蘭迪斯、甘美治、佩利錫等隊友。<br />\n<br />\n古天奴2018年加盟巴塞隆拿後，一直發揮不出在利物浦的水準，今夏加盟拜仁慕尼黑後終於有起色，開季4場聯賽已取得1個入球，而這位巴西國腳也承認在慕尼黑很愜意。<br />\n<br />\n「慕尼黑是一個很好的城市，人們非常友善和熱情。我和家人已經有家的感覺，我覺得拜仁也有同樣的文化：像個大家庭。」古天奴說。拜仁開季聯賽戰績是3勝2和0負，以兩分落後榜首的RB萊比錫。"},{"pid":"a7350e29d5a0bd82b385c5e9700bbc02d5357832","tid":1596303,"uid":45772,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:53:40.000Z","msg":"7-1"},{"pid":"2ec22ed846a07c81aec946d15888a8804521ee65","tid":1596303,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:56:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"852ebb9f24729e46389793e888d334894aade3b2","tid":1596303,"uid":23140,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a7350e29d5a0bd82b385c5e9700bbc02d5357832","tid":1596303,"uid":45772,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:53:40.000Z","msg":"7-1"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T12:57:03.000Z","msg":"25古邊會記得國恥<br />\n隊隊波都係不能拒絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3134ce0493aebb7922047f72af4ea57a13ce0e3","tid":1596303,"uid":25754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T13:00:27.000Z","msg":"25仔嚟港超食蛋撻啦"},{"pid":"f9edd8549009af5de2c104a3c8e39af271b91012","tid":1596303,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime